OL,3,CSenior officer to face misconduct
OL,4,Cmeeting for Manchester Arena response
OL,6,FA senior police officer involved in
OL,7,Fcoordinating the tactical police
OL,8,Fresponse to the Manchester Arena
OL,9,Fbombing in 2017 will face a misconduct
OL,10,Fmeeting.
OL,12,FIt comes after families of those who
OL,13,Fdied in the attack on 22 May 2017 made
OL,14,Fa complaint to Greater Manchester
OL,15,FPolice (GMP) about the actions and
OL,16,Fdecision-making of the officer on the
OL,17,Fnight.
OL,19,FThat complaint was then referred on to
OL,20,Fpolice watchdog, the Independent
OL,21,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC).
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
