OL,3,CSenior officer to face misconduct
OL,4,Cmeeting for Manchester Arena response
OL,6,FIt was alleged that the unnamed
OL,7,Fofficer had failed to alert others
OL,8,Fthey were not sufficiently skilled,
OL,9,Fexperienced or knowledgable to be able
OL,10,Fto effectively fulfil the role of
OL,11,Fcoordinating the police response.
OL,13,FIn May 2024, the officer was served
OL,14,Fwith a formal notice that their
OL,15,Fconduct was under investigation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
