OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F397A1758309918
OL,3,CSenior officer to face misconduct
OL,4,Cmeeting for Manchester Arena response
OL,6,FThe IOPC says the misconduct meeting
OL,7,Fwould be held for the officer due to
OL,8,F"potential breaches of the police
OL,9,Fstandards of professional behaviour
OL,10,Frelating to integrity, duties and
OL,11,Fresponsibilities, and discreditable
OL,12,Fconduct".
OL,14,FUnlike a misconduct hearing, a meeting
OL,15,Fis held in private and officers can
OL,16,Freceive a sanction ranging up to a
OL,17,Ffinal written warning.
OL,19,FA complaint was made to GMP on 28
OL,20,FAugust 2021 by family members who lost
OL,21,Ftheir loved ones on the night.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
