OL,4,Cmeeting for Manchester Arena response
OL,6,FThis was then referred to the IOPC on
OL,7,F2 September 2021 for further
OL,8,Finvestigation.
OL,10,FThe IOPC has also recommended that GMP
OL,11,Fmake an apology to the complainants
OL,12,Ffor the "shortcomings on the night of
OL,13,Fthe attack," including explanation of
OL,14,Fhow the force will prevent similar
OL,15,Fissues in the future.
OL,17,FArrangements for disciplinary
OL,18,Fproceedings will now take place.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
