OL,3,CSenior officer to face misconduct
OL,4,Cmeeting for Manchester Arena response
OL,6,F22 people died and hundreds were
OL,7,Finjured when a bomb was detonated at
OL,8,Fthe end of an Ariana Grande concert at
OL,9,FManchester Arena.
OL,11,FIOPC Director Amanda Rowe said: "Our
OL,12,Finvestigation follows the tragic
OL,13,Fincident on 22 May 2017 when a bomb
OL,14,Fwas detonated at the Manchester Arena
OL,15,Fin which 22 people sadly lost their
OL,16,Flives.
OL,18,F"Our thoughts remain with all those
OL,19,Faffected` a tragedy that will forever
OL,20,Fhave a profound impact right across
OL,21,FGreater Manchester and beyond.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
