OL,3,CSenior officer to face misconduct
OL,4,Cmeeting for Manchester Arena response
OL,6,F"It was vital for public confidence in
OL,7,Fpolicing that such matters were
OL,8,Fsubject to thorough and independent
OL,9,Fscrutiny and our independent
OL,10,Finvestigation looked into a complaint
OL,11,Fregarding the actions and decision -
OL,12,Fmaking of a senior Greater Manchester
OL,13,FPolice officer on the night of the
OL,14,Fattack.
OL,16,F"It will now be for a police
OL,17,Fdisciplinary panel to consider the
OL,18,Fevidence and reach a decision based on
OL,19,Fall the available information."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
