OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F397A1758309918
OL,3,CSenior officer to face misconduct
OL,4,Cmeeting for Manchester Arena response
OL,6,F"I want to reiterate the Chief
OL,7,FConstable's unreserved apology made on
OL,8,Fbehalf of GMP to the families
OL,9,Ffollowing the public inquiry.
OL,11,F"We are steadfast in our commitment to
OL,12,Fensure we do not repeat the
OL,13,Finadequacies identified in the public
OL,14,Finquiry.
OL,16,F"We have worked extensively in the
OL,17,Fyears since to continue cementing the
OL,18,Fsubstantive improvements made as a
OL,19,Fresult of the recommendations made."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
